g.title: EleanorRank1Convo1 begins.
g.text: EleanorRank1Convo1 begins.

g.title: j571060905
g.text: Eleanor?

g.title: j2008525619
g.text: Mmm?

g.title: j3563285523
g.text: Why do you even use this? You can talk telepathically, right?

g.title: j3845581328
g.text: Just how infested ARE you?

g.title: j1519663701
g.text: Just checking you're alive. [End.]

g.title: j1508111534
g.text: Shrewd question.

g.title: j500968428
g.text: Are you asking out of concern, or idle curiosity?

g.title: j4175782925
g.text: Alive and now mildly annoyed.

g.title: j961001693
g.text: It’s about two things, honestly. Control and art.

g.title: j2104006938
g.text: Concern.

g.title: j1166033459
g.text: Idle curiosity. [End.]

g.title: j3900199445
g.text: Cheerio.

g.title: j2588263555
g.text: Telepathy doesn’t give you control?

g.title: j3507485732
g.text: How is a chat message 'art'?

g.title: j3500097578
g.text: Ah. How sweet.

g.title: j1493112118
g.text: Can I suggest you find something else with which to occupy your time?

g.title: Chat ends.
g.text: Chat ends.

g.title: j140615416
g.text: Look. I was raised to be polite. It’s a Britannic thing.

g.title: j4059585968
g.text: Because I have to compose every sentence. I don’t just get to dump meaning wholesale into your head.

g.title: j3299509259
g.text: I am, after all, the very picture of frailty.

g.title: j173597260
g.text: Try prancing up to Arthur and asking about his haemorrhoids.

g.title: j2899550050
g.text: Politeness is all about not letting the other person know how you feel about them.

g.title: j362123797
g.text: That would be easy. Lazy. Uninteresting.

g.title: j1645810272
g.text: Perhaps you'd like to mop my brow as I recline upon my fainting couch?

g.title: j3457642309
g.text: This is your first and only warning. I am not an exhibit.

g.title: j940871138
g.text: Which is hard, when your mind is effectively plugged into theirs.

g.title: j2002074335
g.text: Telepathy is about as nuanced as a boot up the arse.

g.title: j356429573
g.text: Perhaps.

g.title: j4232920086
g.text: I didn't say it was concern for YOU. [End.]

g.title: j2567629148
g.text: For instance, right now I could be feeling like wrapping your guts around a stick...

g.title: j2177821983
g.text: By comparison, text is fascinating.

g.title: j859312772
g.text: +10 Chemistry

g.title: j192012106
g.text: Ah! You are being circumspect. Treating me as the fearsome lamia I am.

g.title: j73231669
g.text: ... or feeling giddy as a schoolgirl because you’re finally talking to me.

g.title: j3644318738
g.text: Largely because of what it doesn’t say.

g.title: j3243427506
g.text: Careful.

g.title: j477909008
g.text: You should have met me BEFORE I was infested.

g.title: j961557494
g.text: You don’t know. But if this were a telepathic conversation, you would.

g.title: j960032540
g.text: 'Read between the lines'?

g.title: j154963874
g.text: I bite.

g.title: j4193866608
g.text: So it's about not showing your feelings?

g.title: j351857570
g.text: Sounds like you just prefer to hide behind a screen. [End.]

g.title: j839211622
g.text: Exactly. Before Höllvania, before the Techrot, I depended on text to make my living. Now it’s just a luxury. A whimsy.

g.title: j3964011462
g.text: Until I choose to, yes. Perhaps it's silly to try to be civilized in this shithole. But...

g.title: j1688551038
g.text: Can you blame me for taking every inch of privacy I can get?

g.title: j1334330620
g.text: Something to play with.

g.title: j3075472939
g.text: +20 Chemistry

g.title: j3830011099
g.text: Clearly I made the right choice.

g.title: j3241390025
g.text: To pass the time while I wait for my body to turn into a chimera I barely recognize.

g.title: j4094487119
g.text: ... we all have our little ways of staying sane, don't we?

g.title: j2237655961
g.text: Does it help?

g.title: j3916995640
g.text: Um... have fun with that. [End.]

g.title: j517783173
g.text: Oh, yes. After all...
